---
import ApiPageHeader from "../components/ApiPageHeader.astro";

const markdown = `# Limitations

What this API does not do or claim:

- Self-hosted runtime host only. No hosted service, upload, publication, account, or sync.
- Detector output is not transcription, understanding, or translation.
- Coverage, citation closure, receipt integrity, and structural QC are not semantic quality.
- Private captions and artifacts are not publication.
- No self-improvement gain is claimed.
`;
---

<section class="api-section" aria-labelledby="api-nonclaims-heading">
  <ApiPageHeader
    title="Limitations"
    headingId="api-nonclaims-heading"
    description="What this API does not do or claim."
    markdown={markdown}
  />
  <ul class="api-list">
    <li>
      This is a self-hosted runtime host. No hosted service, upload, publication, account, or sync
      exists.
    </li>
    <li>
      Detector output — speech activity, language ranges, acoustic classes, speaker clusters,
      separation stems — is not transcription, understanding, or translation.
    </li>
    <li>Coverage, citation closure, receipt integrity, and structural QC are not semantic quality.</li>
    <li>Private captions and artifacts are not publication.</li>
    <li>
      No self-improvement gain is claimed. The measurement machinery exists; a proven gain does
      not yet.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <div class="api-links">
    <a class="button button-primary" href="/benchmarks/">Benchmarks</a>
    <a class="button button-quiet" href="/method/">Method</a>
  </div>
</section>
